fn.p:
Abbreviations: Au: gold nanoparticles;
XOR: xanthine oxidoreductase; fMWCNT: functionalized multiwalled carbon
nanotube; PEDOT: poly(3,4-ethylenedioxythiophene); GCE: glassy carbon
electrode; XODNPs: xanthine oxidase nanoparticle; [poly(l-asp):poly(l-aspartic
acid)]; ZnO: zinc oxide; Ch: chitosan; PANI: polyaniline; Pt: platinum;
PPy: polypyrrole; c-MWCNT: carboxylated multiwalled carbon nanotube;
TiO2: titanium dioxide; ITO: indium tin oxide; poly-TTCA:
poly-5,2′:5′,2″-terthiophine-3-carboxylic acid;
CV: cyclic voltammetry; and DPV: differential pulse voltammetry.
